OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778663195
OL,3,CBoy, 15, arrested after teenage girl
OL,4,Cseriously injured in bike crash
OL,6,FThe girl suffered serious injuries
OL,7,Fincluding a fractured jaw, a
OL,8,Flaceration to her forehead and damage
OL,9,Fto her teeth.
OL,11,FPolice said the bike, which is thought
OL,12,Fto have been an e-bike, was taken away
OL,13,Ffrom the scene before officers arrived.
OL,15,FA 15-year-old boy from Southampton has
OL,16,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of drug
OL,17,Fdriving and causing serious injury by
OL,18,Fcareless driving.
OL,20,FHe has been released under
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
